imdb.plot outline: Singing and dancing - Everyone is able to do this! But who has the courage to sing or dance on a big stage in front of a huge audience? CARTOON NETWORK D! HALL OF FAME gives talented children the opportunity to fulfil their dream of performing on a big stage. This show is not about competition and pressure to perform but rather about the joy of singing and dancing.
